title: Couple With Heart Woman Person
description: Depicts a couple consisting of a person and a man, with a heart between them. This emoji signifies a romantic relationship, love, and partnership between a man and a person.
apple_vendor_description: This heartwarming emoji on Apple devices depicts a couple with a vibrant red heart floating between them, rendered with Apple's signature glossy 3D effect and soft, rounded edges. The figures are shown with gentle expressions and warm skin tones, symbolizing a strong bond and affection. Its presence on Apple devices clearly communicates love, romance, and deep connection between two people.
